prompts.frontCover:
A dynamic comic book panel in the style of a classic superhero comic. In the center, a charming cartoon-style illustration of Lao Lao as a superhero, "Super Lao Lao," striking a powerful and funny pose. She wears a vibrant cape and a mask, and is surrounded by energetic action lines and Kirby dots. A smaller, comically awe-struck cartoon figure of her boyfriend, Jordan, is in the bottom corner looking up at her with admiration, holding a birthday cake with lit candles. A large, explosive comic book sound effect bubble like "KAPOW!" or "ZAP!" is near the top of the panel.

Centered in the middle of the design, a large speech bubble contains the greeting text written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script: "Happy Birthday to my Favorite Superhero!"
